{"tid":1458842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［三不］不分化；不割蓆；不篤灰","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:58:14.000Z","uid":152341,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c90ac19629dd69e6dc7e052ace3df58ec5e4f92","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"經過8.11同今日玩狼來了之後，有d人已經開始忘記「三不」，尤其是「不分化」同「不割蓆」。<br />\n<br />\n我知道tg群又好，連登都好都開始充滿mon po 狗或者有意分化我地既人，好似今日為例子，簡直係流料滿天飛，又熄燈，又清場，又cut network咁，有一段時間真係連網都收唔到既時間，只可以靠口傳，有d人就放風係咁叫人走，好多人都因此走左，而我係大概5點左右走，但利申呢個係我原本set 比自己既時間，我冇聽任何叫走既口傳。<br />\n<br />\n今日係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非主場</span></span></strong>，所以好多和理非都今日走出黎，包括我。我諗好多和理非其實都掙扎左好耐先決定今日出黎，因為唔知d狗幾時清場，經過琴晚亦唔知佢地會做d咩出黎，出黎搭巴士果陣其實我仲驚緊，不過為左<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公義</span></strong></span>，我就算臨時請假（利申：返緊工）都係要企出黎發聲。<br />\n<br />\n但係我走既時候係tg群到見到有班仲留守緊既手足係到屌d已經走左既人係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懦夫撚</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話香港冇民主就因為有呢班撚樣</span></span></strong>，不停狂屌班已走既和理非，而最令我心寒既，係我竟然聽到一句<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「驚就咪出黎，返屋企做你既冷氣軍師啦」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請問你同狗有咩分别</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我想講，我唔知你係人定鬼，如果你係人講呢番說話既時間係幾傷和理非既心，和理非唔同勇武，正因為我地已經唔夠勇氣同你地係前線並肩作戰，其實我地已經感到<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好內疚，慚愧</span></span></strong>，而當我地終於可以用我地既方式表達既訴求，對你地既支持既時候，就係因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「唔留守」,「狼來了」</span></strong></span>，就屌鳩我地，我地唔係勇武，你亦都唔好覺得我地會一秒變勇武，我地本來就已經係戰戰兢兢，硬住頭皮咁出黎，如果你地用勇武標準黎屌鳩我地，之後既任何活動由萬人變到得幾十人，冇和理非support你地，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地都有好大責任</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同時，大家都唔好屌d留守人士，話佢地做乜仲留係到等狗暴力清場咩，佢地有佢地既決定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要令兩方都心灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要留要走，都請你尊重</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次有人要走<br />\n請不要說「屌你老母懦夫撚」<br />\n請試著說「我尊重你決定，請小心安全」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次有人要留<br />\n請不要說「屌你老母想食tg呀」[<br />\n請試著說「我尊重你決定，請留意狀況，安全為上」/red]</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]不分化<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不篤灰</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e2a097d70fcbc9f428c6212e71bf4b15a6c98422","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"ad3b7be282ce6ad2aa577b9aa00503ef937a7e75","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"cc91ecfdc07bb5a89d89f67aef5eae851b79406b","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"15ae24d3e59f8a6a53e504034a1014643df461e4","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"b10078976213bf202cf4108d1ae3b6687454b81d","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"6<br />\n不分化呀"},{"pid":"c853f81c79f04ada5a0eef195b04f1adace5bebf","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"5<br />\n不割蓆呀"},{"pid":"807aff650293f921add688f529bdfaa81fe6364a","tid":1458842,"uid":266735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"絕不割蓆"},{"pid":"50500b6d23524d6f87d5badfe9e2b554fb77c93b","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"4<br />\n不篤灰呀"},{"pid":"3777c7b1febd24a04b8cf9d5868dcb2e9e9910d1","tid":1458842,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"673c048e6b977c9862bfaec4db7eaa05bc95c65c","tid":1458842,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5kpCHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5kpCHq.png&h=4602514d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67c9bf3f6b1425930b475bb0faab0b6002c2b5a6","tid":1458842,"uid":11255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"重要重要！<br />\n香港最要界別之一 醫護全面進場！<br />\n巴絲快啲入去幫推！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【代宣傳】【遍地開花】聽日 7 間醫院醫護人員一齊靜坐抗議！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88bb640335fbb25d17fdfd12f08dc952ef9516eb","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"3<br />\n推到玩核彈都唔割呀"},{"pid":"f769ad532fd482e35cafbcbf36b966d625dc288e","tid":1458842,"uid":305390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"909f5963129aa15851ae226c502e2856fda27da0","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n推到你地班契弟團結呀"},{"pid":"ac9f83442ba929fca920fca42e4297e8ccc8ba6a","tid":1458842,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5384dd2e5c13ff5de825aa599c4a5d92efebb01","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n再分化班mon po 狗同藍絲笑鳩我地呀"},{"pid":"47a74854cd1b0d31305e797ba210a895b7dc8b80","tid":1458842,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score